Vulkan PC-bar-nonpriv
"Producer-Consumer pattern using named barriers. 
 Load and store are non-private and thus in locord. 
 Barriers are acq_rel and thus they are not in sw."
{
x=0;
P0:r0=0
}
 P0@sg 0, wg 0, qf 0       | P1@sg 0,wg 0, qf 0        ;
 st.atom.wg.sc0 x, 1       |                           ;
 cbar.acq_rel.wg.semsc0 0  | cbar.acq_rel.wg.semsc0 0  ;
                           | ld.atom.wg.sc0 r0, x      ;
forall
 (P1:r0 == 1)